      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in the garage and treated like royalty. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously loved and cared for, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
