    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a benchmark of mechanical purity. This S54-powered coupe features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS, delivering linear power to a 3.64 limited-slip differential. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual ensures tactile engagement, complemented by a documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing replacement\u2014essential preventive measures for this chassis. Suspension kinematics remain stock and tight, maintaining factory dampening characteristics. The exterior retains its original luster with zero oxidation, while the interior showcases preserved Nappa leather. This is a turn-key enthusiast example with a comprehensive service history and optimized compression across all six cylinders.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
